1ï¸âƒ£ Understanding CoNLL-2003 File Format
CoNLL-2003 dataset is usually in three files:

train.txt â†’ Training data
valid.txt â†’ Validation data
test.txt â†’ Testing data
Each file typically follows this format:

mathematica
Copy
Edit
EU B-ORG
rejects O
the O
call O
of O
Germany B-LOC
...
Columns: [Token] [NER-Tag]

