âœ… Now you can directly use train.csv, val.csv, and test.csv in your NER model!

ğŸ“Œ ğŸš€ Summary: How to Fix This?
Problem	Fix
KeyError: No supported file found	âœ… Use load_dataset("text", data_files=...)
Data is not split into tokens	âœ… Use load_conll_data() function
Need CSV files for training	âœ… Convert into train.csv, val.csv, test.csv
